167
00:11:37,596 --> 00:11:41,828
Phoebe n'a jamais eu
de relation sérieuse...

168
00:11:43,469 --> 00:11:44,959
depuis...

169
00:11:45,137 --> 00:11:49,836
sa relation super sérieuse...

170
00:11:50,042 --> 00:11:51,270
avec...

