182
00:12:53,105 --> 00:12:55,335
Quelle agréable surprise!

183
00:13:03,382 --> 00:13:04,747
J'arrive.

184
00:13:11,991 --> 00:13:13,754
C'était moins une.

185
00:13:18,330 --> 00:13:20,025
